a. Ultimately, the FBI's activities reveal the sustained nature of US imperial ambitions in the Americas.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Sep 2020) 0aEspionage, AmericanzEcuadorxHistoryy20th century. 0aEspionage, AmericanzLatin AmericaxHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / Americas (North, Central, South, West Indies).2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDUK eBook-Package 2017z978311069634940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780822372783zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780822372783423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780822372783.jpg  a978-3-11-069634-9  DUK eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles